<inglise>(11.06.98 entered into force 16.07.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 981) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Loa kehtivus l&otilde;peb ennet&auml;htaegselt, kui j&auml;litusmenetlus l&otilde;petatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 11 s&auml;testatud tingimustel ja korras, v&otilde;i kui kohtunik t&uuml;histab p&otilde;hjendatult loa v&otilde;i kui Justiitsministeeriumi vanglate osakonna juht v&otilde;i tema k&auml;skkirjaga volitatud ametnik otsustab j&auml;lituse erandtoimingu l&otilde;petada. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) Permission shall expire prematurely if a surveillance proceeding is terminated under the conditions and pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect; 11 of this Act, if a judge revokes the permission for a justified reason, or if the head of the Prisons Department of the Ministry of Justice or the official authorised by his or her directive decides to terminate an exceptional surveillance activity. </inglise>
